Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛  最喜歡巴幫我綁頭髮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  綁好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴  快要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚就會回來了  到時候我們再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們說好了哦  這是巴和小雛之間的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能毀約的約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「雛莓」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是三島屋的紅豆泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在很受歡迎的  特地買回來給真紅你吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～吃泡芙的模樣太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  快點出去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…再讓我待一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  她真是個好神奇的人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想抱抱看～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去泡紅茶給我喝  我不要喝溫的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是姐弟  兩個都一樣不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把窗戶關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有窗戶啦  都是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～你把一切都毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我可什麼都沒弄壞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然能若無其事地說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是靜不下來的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…你是怎麼辦到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這種事都要我說明嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡無法安靜的喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒答應要當你的僕從哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那扇門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門嗎？可是這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話  打開就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張桌子真特別  我還是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間雖然很小  不過我喜歡這裡的香水味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我把茶端到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫馬桶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下來  大便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後沖水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害羞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你多少也有可愛的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是學校發的講義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  總是麻煩你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要不要進來喝杯茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  我還有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻煩了  我真的已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的臉色還是很差
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯茶再走也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地走到這裡來  一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是班長的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴當上班長了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…要不要嘗嘗這個泡芙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面包著紅豆卡士達餡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能到這裡來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  為什麼不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要問了  把這個戴上  絕對不能在巴面前說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是新型的貓耳娃娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  尤其是耳朵還會動啊動的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真紅  你在哪裡？真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然擅自跑出房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷裡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  來一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  今天晚上跟我睡好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純有時候會變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續好幾天叫他都沒有反應…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這種時候暫時讓他一個人靜一靜比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙人  巴你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說傍晚會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說要跟小雛一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還答應我絕對不會毀約
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴  過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那個人也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說馬上就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小雛關在皮箱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一直…一直…一直沒回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會那麼做的  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再孤單一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠跟我在一起吧  永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛…雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:10:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候不要管他比較好是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  什麼？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…流星？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望純能快點好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望純能快點好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望純…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是狸貓  就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶？  這點小事自己想辦法處理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是那件事怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星有沒有到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  讓我許一個願望就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  紀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家裡有沒有大一點的鏡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個應該可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成擁有生命碎片的  以及沒有生命碎片的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這面鏡子擁有這樣的素質
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不好意思  我很笨  所以對物理方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了  是恩格爾係數法則對不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？現在？你一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有媒介跟在身邊的話  我還是可以堅持30分鐘的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟純說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是叫我讓他靜一靜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…書裡面是那麼寫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正瞭解純的  不是書本而是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純自己會找到正確的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在他看起來有點迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他找到答案之前  你就陪在他身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤零零一個人  迷失自己的孩子是很可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著他不管的話  會招來無法挽救的後果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓  求求你  讓我回去原來的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？  巴你討厭跟我在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣  不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以又逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴答應要跟小雛在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧  巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見  雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  真紅也是來陪我們玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都是紀拖拖拉拉的  搞的我這麼狼狽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來是為了…愛麗絲遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛想跟巴再玩得久一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那麼在遊戲獲勝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp160}　{\fsp1}Rosa Mystica\N{\r}愛麗絲遊戲是爭奪彼此薔薇聖母的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸的人會變成不能動也不能說話的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏的人就能朝「愛麗絲」更接近一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們薔薇少女注定的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你沒有自信贏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  你太壞心眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點進步都沒有的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都用哭鬧耍賴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣  你才會變成孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭真紅  壞真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛要把你打扁！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變得這麼熱  估計是她又跟奇怪的人偶戰鬥了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…絕對不會輸的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖聽話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有媒介在身邊  威力也會減半是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛要是輸了  就得跟巴分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要跟巴分開！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏…贏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能跟巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓  你從巴身上奪取太多力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去她會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  巴  巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  巴  睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛不會再哭鬧  也不會再耍脾氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那麼想救她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛把自己的薔薇聖母給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先不用那麼衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要薔薇聖母  是由我來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  如果沒有戒指  小雛什麼力量都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  什麼事都辦不到  只是個普通的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了30分鐘了  怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正瞭解純的  不是書本而是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅一直沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說這個房間的鏡子好像是什麼入口處之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她在這裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是幹什麼啊  不要擅自做一些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都跟紀說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果你也跟我一起來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰理你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲帶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙果然去打鬥了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫雛莓  從今天起是我的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛不喜歡陰暗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這可不行  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是要說  那傢伙也要住在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  因為她是我的僕從啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要住在這裡伺候我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不答應  我絕對不答應！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  已經9點03分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上是睡覺的時間  純也快去睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你怎麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  給我打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真紅！你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你睡…  真紅！給我打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  要跟小雛一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我真紅大人  因為你是我的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  要玩女王遊戲對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不跟小雛玩  小雛就不把軟軟的分給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:23:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟軟的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟軟的就是軟軟的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這只薔薇戒指發誓吧
